song_lyrics: Jyun jyun kaḍake khaḍake thaḍake, faḍake morī chhatiyā... °ṭek
Garajat gagan saghan ghaṭā ghankī, chau dish āī chaḍake... ° 1
Bolat dādur mor papīharā, hiyarā morā dhaḍake... ° 2
Bish andhiyārī hu sukumārī, taḍtaḍ bījurī taḍake... ° 3
Premānand kahe niṭhur Nāthku, ko samujāve laḍake... ° 4
title: Jyu jyu kaḍake khaḍake thaḍake
